'''MaxSec Eight''' was a maximum security [[Space station/Legends|space station]] detention center shaped like a cylinder, which held the crew of the ''[[Avengeance]]'' after their capture searching for [[Zonama Sekot/Legends|Zonama Sekot]], as well as the [[Pirate/Legends|pirate]] [[Redstar]].

